WEBVTT

NOTE Running gag sequence of 'You're no fun anymore' lines and return to the spotter.

00:02:19.500 --> 00:02:22.500
<v Spotter>
Oh, you're no fun anymore.

00:02:22.500 --> 00:02:27.500
[action] ANIMATION: Girl in bed with Dracula whose fangs fall out.

00:02:27.500 --> 00:02:29.500
<v Girl>
Oh, you're no fun anymore.

00:02:29.500 --> 00:02:33.500
[action] A man at the yardarm being lashed.

00:02:33.500 --> 00:02:36.000
<v Lasher>
.. thirty-nine… forty. All right, cut him down, Mr Fuller.

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:38.500
<v Lashee>
Oh you're no fun anymore.

00:02:38.500 --> 00:02:43.000
[action] Back to camel spotter.

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:47.000
<v Spotter>
Now if anybody else pinches my phrase I'll throw them under a camel.

00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:50.000
<v Interviewer>
(giggling) If you can spot one.

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:56.000
[action] Spotter glares. Knight in armour appears and hits interviewer with a chicken.

